data.description: Prime location in close proximity to everything that Bayview & Milwaukee's Lakefront offers! Privacy abounds this sprawling COLONIAL which is perfectly situated on nearly a 1/4 acre lot. Exterior boasts a fenced in yard,  multi-level decks + an oversized shed! Step inside to find an open concept layout showcasing the HUGE kitchen/dining area complete with a double oven, a surplus of cabinets, equipped with pull out drawers, and a center island/breakfast nook. Living room proudly displays a natural fireplace and HUGE bay window w/window seat! In addition find first floor laundry + a sun-filled 4 season room! Head upstairs to find 3 LARGE bedrooms + a walk-out porch! PERFECT mix of character & upgrades! TONS of big ticket items completed including replacement windows throughout! Welcome Home
